=======
RULES
=======

// @rule cannot_push_crate
// @emits push_crate_failed
[ > Player | Crate ] -> CANCEL
[ > Player | Wall ] -> CANCEL

// @rule pull_single_crate
// @emits pull_crate
// The player moves away from an adjacent crate, pulling it into the old player cell.
[ Crate | > Player | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ > Crate | > Player | ]

// Direction markers preserve the attempted portal entry direction until late rules.
right [ > Player | PortalA ] -> [ > Player | PortalA DirRight ]
left [ > Player | PortalA ] -> [ > Player | PortalA DirLeft ]
up [ > Player | PortalA ] -> [ > Player | PortalA DirUp ]
down [ > Player | PortalA ] -> [ > Player | PortalA DirDown ]

right [ > Player | PortalB ] -> [ > Player | PortalB DirRight ]
left [ > Player | PortalB ] -> [ > Player | PortalB DirLeft ]
up [ > Player | PortalB ] -> [ > Player | PortalB DirUp ]
down [ > Player | PortalB ] -> [ > Player | PortalB DirDown ]

right [ > Player | PortalD ] -> [ > Player | PortalD DirRight ]
left [ > Player | PortalD ] -> [ > Player | PortalD DirLeft ]
up [ > Player | PortalD ] -> [ > Player | PortalD DirUp ]
down [ > Player | PortalD ] -> [ > Player | PortalD DirDown ]

right [ > Player | PortalE ] -> [ > Player | PortalE DirRight ]
left [ > Player | PortalE ] -> [ > Player | PortalE DirLeft ]
up [ > Player | PortalE ] -> [ > Player | PortalE DirUp ]
down [ > Player | PortalE ] -> [ > Player | PortalE DirDown ]

right [ > Player | PortalH ] -> [ > Player | PortalH DirRight ]
left [ > Player | PortalH ] -> [ > Player | PortalH DirLeft ]
up [ > Player | PortalH ] -> [ > Player | PortalH DirUp ]
down [ > Player | PortalH ] -> [ > Player | PortalH DirDown ]

right [ > Player | PortalI ] -> [ > Player | PortalI DirRight ]
left [ > Player | PortalI ] -> [ > Player | PortalI DirLeft ]
up [ > Player | PortalI ] -> [ > Player | PortalI DirUp ]
down [ > Player | PortalI ] -> [ > Player | PortalI DirDown ]

// @rule enter_portal.normal_teleport
// @emits portal_enter portal_teleport
late right [ Player PortalA DirRight ] [ PortalB | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalA ] [ PortalB | Player Done ]
late left  [ Player PortalA DirLeft  ] [ PortalB | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalA ] [ PortalB | Player Done ]
late up    [ Player PortalA DirUp    ] [ PortalB | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalA ] [ PortalB | Player Done ]
late down  [ Player PortalA DirDown  ] [ PortalB | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalA ] [ PortalB | Player Done ]

late right [ Player PortalB DirRight ] [ PortalA | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalB ] [ PortalA | Player Done ]
late left  [ Player PortalB DirLeft  ] [ PortalA | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalB ] [ PortalA | Player Done ]
late up    [ Player PortalB DirUp    ] [ PortalA | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalB ] [ PortalA | Player Done ]
late down  [ Player PortalB DirDown  ] [ PortalA | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalB ] [ PortalA | Player Done ]

late right [ Player PortalD DirRight ] [ PortalE | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalD ] [ PortalE | Player Done ]
late left  [ Player PortalD DirLeft  ] [ PortalE | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalD ] [ PortalE | Player Done ]
late up    [ Player PortalD DirUp    ] [ PortalE | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalD ] [ PortalE | Player Done ]
late down  [ Player PortalD DirDown  ] [ PortalE | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalD ] [ PortalE | Player Done ]

late right [ Player PortalE DirRight ] [ PortalD | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalE ] [ PortalD | Player Done ]
late left  [ Player PortalE DirLeft  ] [ PortalD | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalE ] [ PortalD | Player Done ]
late up    [ Player PortalE DirUp    ] [ PortalD | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalE ] [ PortalD | Player Done ]
late down  [ Player PortalE DirDown  ] [ PortalD | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalE ] [ PortalD | Player Done ]

late right [ Player PortalH DirRight ] [ PortalI | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalH ] [ PortalI | Player Done ]
late left  [ Player PortalH DirLeft  ] [ PortalI | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalH ] [ PortalI | Player Done ]
late up    [ Player PortalH DirUp    ] [ PortalI | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalH ] [ PortalI | Player Done ]
late down  [ Player PortalH DirDown  ] [ PortalI | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalH ] [ PortalI | Player Done ]

late right [ Player PortalI DirRight ] [ PortalH | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalI ] [ PortalH | Player Done ]
late left  [ Player PortalI DirLeft  ] [ PortalH | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalI ] [ PortalH | Player Done ]
late up    [ Player PortalI DirUp    ] [ PortalH | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalI ] [ PortalH | Player Done ]
late down  [ Player PortalI DirDown  ] [ PortalH | no Blocking no Player ] -> [ PortalI ] [ PortalH | Player Done ]

// @rule enter_portal.blocked_exit_push_entrance
// @emits portal_enter portal_exit_blocked portal_fallback_push
// If the paired portal's exit cell is blocked, push the entrance portal instead.
late right [ Player PortalA DirRight | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalB | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalA Done ] [ PortalB | Blocking ]
late left  [ Player PortalA DirLeft  | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalB | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalA Done ] [ PortalB | Blocking ]
late up    [ Player PortalA DirUp    | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalB | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalA Done ] [ PortalB | Blocking ]
late down  [ Player PortalA DirDown  | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalB | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalA Done ] [ PortalB | Blocking ]

late right [ Player PortalB DirRight | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalA | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalB Done ] [ PortalA | Blocking ]
late left  [ Player PortalB DirLeft  | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalA | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalB Done ] [ PortalA | Blocking ]
late up    [ Player PortalB DirUp    | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalA | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalB Done ] [ PortalA | Blocking ]
late down  [ Player PortalB DirDown  | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalA | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalB Done ] [ PortalA | Blocking ]

late right [ Player PortalD DirRight | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalE | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalD Done ] [ PortalE | Blocking ]
late left  [ Player PortalD DirLeft  | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalE | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalD Done ] [ PortalE | Blocking ]
late up    [ Player PortalD DirUp    | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalE | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalD Done ] [ PortalE | Blocking ]
late down  [ Player PortalD DirDown  | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalE | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalD Done ] [ PortalE | Blocking ]

late right [ Player PortalE DirRight | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalD | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalE Done ] [ PortalD | Blocking ]
late left  [ Player PortalE DirLeft  | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalD | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalE Done ] [ PortalD | Blocking ]
late up    [ Player PortalE DirUp    | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalD | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalE Done ] [ PortalD | Blocking ]
late down  [ Player PortalE DirDown  | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalD | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalE Done ] [ PortalD | Blocking ]

late right [ Player PortalH DirRight | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalI | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalH Done ] [ PortalI | Blocking ]
late left  [ Player PortalH DirLeft  | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalI | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalH Done ] [ PortalI | Blocking ]
late up    [ Player PortalH DirUp    | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalI | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalH Done ] [ PortalI | Blocking ]
late down  [ Player PortalH DirDown  | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalI | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalH Done ] [ PortalI | Blocking ]

late right [ Player PortalI DirRight | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalH | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalI Done ] [ PortalH | Blocking ]
late left  [ Player PortalI DirLeft  | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalH | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalI Done ] [ PortalH | Blocking ]
late up    [ Player PortalI DirUp    | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalH | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalI Done ] [ PortalH | Blocking ]
late down  [ Player PortalI DirDown  | no Blocking no Player ] [ PortalH | Blocking ] -> [ Player | PortalI Done ] [ PortalH | Blocking ]

// Crate-goal levels use the same Done-based win adapter.
late [ Crate Target ] -> [ Crate Target Done ]
late [ Player Target ] -> [ Player Target Done ]

// Clean up stale markers when no portal adapter rule consumed them.
late [ Marker ] -> []

// Exported knowledge ids:
// - K_pull_single_crate: 玩家可以把身后相邻的单个箱子向自己的移动方向拉动。
// - K_cannot_push_crate: 玩家不能推动前方的箱子。
// - K_pull_opens_path: 玩家可以通过拉开堵路箱子制造通路。
// - K_portal_teleports_player: 玩家进入出口未堵塞的传送门时会被传送到配对传送门出口。
// - K_blocked_portal_stops_teleport: 传送门出口被堵住时，玩家不会正常传送。
// - K_blocked_portal_pushes_entrance: 传送门出口被堵住且入口传送门前方可移动时，进入入口会改为推动入口传送门。
// - K_blocked_portal_push_can_fail: 如果传送门出口被堵住且入口传送门也推不动，那么进入传送门的动作失败。
// - K_use_crate_to_block_portal_exit: 玩家可以故意把箱子拉到传送门出口，从而触发堵塞出口行为。
// - K_move_portal_to_open_path: 玩家可以利用堵塞出口的 fallback 推动入口传送门，从而改变可达区域。

=============
WINCONDITIONS
=============

Some Done

